The package boost-static-string is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS static_string)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::static_string)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_static_string REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::static_string)
